@startuml overview
title iDaVIE God Class Overview
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor White
    BorderColor #555555
    ArrowColor #555555
}
skinparam package {
    BackgroundColor #F0F4FF
    BorderColor #8888CC
}
hide empty members

package "Data Layer" {

    class VolumeDataSet {
        .. FITS loading ..
        .. WCS coordinates ..
        .. Statistics / histograms ..
        .. GPU texture generation ..
        .. Mask edit and undo ..
        .. FITS export ..
    }

}

package "Rendering Layer" {

    class VolumeDataSetRenderer <<MonoBehaviour>> {
        .. Rendering config ..
        .. Mask rendering ..
        .. Foveated rendering ..
        .. Vignette config ..
        .. Coordinate mapping ..
        .. Region and cursor selection ..
        .. Rest frequency management ..
    }

}

package "VR Interaction Layer" {

    class VolumeInputController <<MonoBehaviour>> {
        .. SteamVR input wiring ..
        .. VR locomotion and scaling ..
        .. Vignette feedback ..
        .. Brush painting ..
        .. Interaction state machine ..
        .. Feature and region editing ..
        .. Video recording ..
    }

}

package "Desktop UI Layer" {

    class CanvassDesktop <<MonoBehaviour>> {
        .. File loading ..
        .. Subset selection ..
        .. Colormap and scaling ..
        .. Thresholds ..
        .. Rest frequency ..
        .. Statistics display ..
        .. Source mapping ..
    }

    class DesktopPaintController <<MonoBehaviour>> {
        .. Slice view and cameras ..
        .. Polygon selection ..
        .. Mask painting ..
        .. Source and color mapping ..
    }

}

VolumeDataSetRenderer --> VolumeDataSet : owns
VolumeInputController --> VolumeDataSetRenderer : drives
CanvassDesktop --> VolumeDataSetRenderer : configures
CanvassDesktop --> VolumeDataSet : loads data into
DesktopPaintController --> VolumeDataSet : paints mask voxels

@enduml
